summary: The document is a form related to the JFK assassination investigation, specifically a record of interview involving Richard C. Nagell and Victor L. Trinkala. It includes agency information, document details, and a cover sheet, indicating it's part of a series of records under the DOD-affiliated personnel and incident investigations. The document is marked as unclassified and was released with deletions on 03/09/95.
key_findings: The document is associated with the JFK assassination investigation.
